{"tid":1128054,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"安祖蓮娜擬分9億予柬埔寨養子Maddox 惹畢彼特不滿","createTime":"2019-04-27T14:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T05:30:56.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"24277c3b526008b5aa49c7127e70f122e455c9ee","tid":1128054,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"荷里活男星畢彼特（Brad Pitt） 與女星安祖蓮娜祖莉（Angelina Jolie） 在2016年9月宣布離婚，對於6名子女的撫養權及財產分配等細節一直未能達成協議。二人早前獲法院批准正式回復單身。近日有報道指17歲長子Maddox在二人婚變期間力撐媽媽，傳安祖蓮娜打算將其電影製作公司留給麥杜斯（Maddox），1.16億美元（約9.09億港元）資產都將由他一人獨得。有傳畢彼特不滿安祖蓮娜對Maddox極度偏心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/angelina-jolie-brad-pitt-700x457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fangelina-jolie-brad-pitt-700x457.jpg&h=5d37bf62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與前夫於柬埔寨孤兒院領養<br />\n畢彼特與安祖蓮娜祖莉的6名子女中，有3名是養子養女，其餘都是畢安所生，另外除最年幼的龍鳳胎外，其餘的兒女都在不同地方出生。Maddox是安祖蓮娜與前夫Billy Bob Thorton於2002年在柬埔寨一所孤兒院中領養的兒子。Maddox之前已在安祖蓮娜執導的Netflix電影《他們先殺了我父親：柬埔寨女孩的回憶》（First They Killed My Father）做過掛名監製，主打豬肉菜式，以厚切豬扒闖出名堂，素有口碑。消息人士透露：「Maddox將主導安祖蓮娜的電影公司，她想將自己的事業傳給他。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/11/03/03/5718544-6348573-image-m-15_1541215001408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F11%2F03%2F03%2F5718544-6348573-image-m-15_1541215001408.jpg&h=2c518ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cheatsheet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/GettyImages-845781102-683x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cheatsheet.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FGettyImages-845781102-683x1024.jpg&h=4ed5dd44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報道，安祖蓮娜與畢彼特在離婚官司期間一直有Maddox陪伴，增加了她對Maddox的信任，消息人士表示：「他選擇站在媽媽這邊，讓安祖蓮娜決定讓他繼承電影事業。」加上她健康狀況欠佳，更加深對兒子的依賴。"},{"pid":"4cbabf8d11af1e580b31526c7987fb9d20f20182","tid":1128054,"uid":77277,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"有無屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f1793fa0d1d4a8f5c7291e998b099331a0919f","tid":1128054,"uid":4502,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"Maddox之前已在安祖蓮娜執導的Netflix電影《他們先殺了我父親：柬埔寨女孩的回憶》（First They Killed My Father）做過掛名監製，主打豬肉菜式，以厚切豬扒闖出名堂，素有口碑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76064d7322ae23f4d04d7c16c80c861a2d61ceea","tid":1128054,"uid":103325,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"主打豬肉菜式，以厚切豬扒闖出名堂，素有口碑。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644932e5aca75fda8660ec32cc27177f9d15a1a0","tid":1128054,"uid":39316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"窮過就會發展出，對機會既嗅覺同埋把握機會既行動力"},{"pid":"6090406b4c4b4be02830aca39a66c0aa81885a28","tid":1128054,"uid":168716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"可能係真愛呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年盜墓者羅拉真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12244442bdfabc821b5bb10117a41af2c8eca59","tid":1128054,"uid":30708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"幾時收養埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcfa7092264ef726b1706c4c939d0e3d302d92e","tid":1128054,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04